      <p class="svc-content-body">We work with <strong>vinyl, composite, and wood siding</strong> to suit every budget and aesthetic. Whether you're re-siding an older home, building new, or patching storm damage, our team delivers clean installs with proper flashing, moisture barriers, and tight finishing that keeps the weather where it belongs &mdash; outside.</p>
      <p class="svc-content-body">Every project starts with a free on-site assessment. We walk the exterior with you, identify problem areas, talk through material options, and provide an honest quote with no hidden costs.</p>
